---------------------------------------------------
|0 |HASH DISTINCT      |    |3       |7           |
|1 |└─HASH JOIN        |    |4       |6           |
|2 |  ├─TABLE FULL SCAN|v1  |4       |3           |
|3 |  └─TABLE FULL SCAN|tmp |4       |3           |
===================================================
